data.description: OPEN HOUSE Sat 11-1 and Sun12-2. Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom raised ranch. Upon entering, you'll be captivated by the abundance of natural daylight that fills the home, highlighting the gorgeous original wood floors. The spacious open concept living area seamlessly connects the kitchen, living room & dining area making it an ideal space for entertaining. The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, featuring custom cabinetry, a farmhouse sink, gas range, double oven, pantry & an oversized island. The primary en-suite includes a custom tiled shower, dual sinks & closets.  Custom tiled main bath. Walk in closets. Finished lower-level w/ a non-conforming bonus room, full bath, spacious laundry room & storage cabinets. Washer/Dryer incl. Large backyard w/shed . Close to Fontenelle Forest. This rare gem in Bellevue must be seen to believe it!
